                    int Search_Bin(SSTable ST, KeyType key, int high, int low){
                        mid = (high, low);
                        if(EQ(key, ST.elem[mid].key))
                            return mid;
                        else if(LT(key, ST.elem[mid].key))
                            Search_Bin(ST, key, mid - 1, low);
                        else
                            Search_Bin(ST, key, mid, low + 1)
                    }
